Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on analyzing image features for training an autonomous vehicle controller using deep learning.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for training the controller.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is another likely category as the paper deals with autonomous vehicles and their controllers.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses deep learning-based approaches for training the controller.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper deals with controlling autonomous vehicles.
